{"Briefly summarize the manufacturing process(es) in the facility:": {"name": "brieflySummarize", "answer": "Crude pea protein is received and stored, then fed into the production line for grinding and size grading. The material is separated and refined through air classification, cyclone separation, and filtration systems. The product is further processed by granulation or powder handling, followed by sieving, metal detection, and magnetic separation. Final products are packed in plastic bags or jumbo bags, labeled, stored, and transported under controlled conditions. Clean filtered air is used throughout the process, and no chemical solvents are applied"}},
